reviewText: I liked the entire Cannon series. Iwas unable to watch the episodes on television due to Military duty. Outstanding series.
If you love cannon you will love this

I love the Cannon series, but this box set is a total nightmare! it stops all the time. Disks are marked up, as if the set were a used.
Season four was even worse, What did the seller do, microwave them?
Not bad, not as good as previous series
It skipped and stalled- not watchable. Like a bootleg DVD. Seasons 1 through 3 were not this poor of quality.
love this show and got it at a price

Great TV show.. But this is a cheap deal...
And they leave the CC closed Caption off of it.. It's on the first two seasons.
But this cheap Co. does not want to take the time/money to keep it on the rest of the seasons..
And yes they could of got it. It's on it all ready... They just don't want to pay for the rights.
